location.fullValue: 321 S Martin Luther King Jr Ave

data.description: Prepare to be captivated by this stunning, expansive, and thoroughly modernized residence, meticulously crafted with impeccable attention to detail. Nestled on a quiet street, this delightful two-story home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms across nearly 2880 sq. ft., with additional potential awaiting your inspiration in the full basement.    Every aspect of this home has been thoughtfully renewed, from the plumbing and electricity to the HVAC system, windows, doors, floors, trims, cabinets, light fixtures, garage door and floor, and even the concrete around the driveway. The kitchen is a masterpiece of contemporary design, featuring exquisite granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a generously sized island perfect for hosting gatherings.    Upstairs, prepare to be amazed by two full bathrooms, including one in the luxurious master suite. The first floor offers a seamless open layout, including a cozy fireplace in the living room, a bright dining room, a kitchen flooded with natural light from two patio doors, a hallway, a convenient half bath, and a laundry area.    Outside, a spacious fenced lot awaits, providing ample room for entertaining, relaxation, and grilling. Rest easy knowing that all renovations were conducted with proper permits and village inspections. This unparalleled gem sets a new standard for luxury living in the area, making it truly one-of-a-kind.
